    "name": "神来之笔：心之奇旅",
    "steam_appid": 1858810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "官方QQ群：763769813<br><br>谨以此感谢我的父亲：幼时，他赠送的我的第一支以“神奇”为名的画笔是这个游戏最初的起源！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/d98ec2ab23665ff828d4c25ce415b837.avif?t=1770118001\" width=592 height=75 /></span><br><br>《神来之笔》是一款超现实主义的动作平台游戏，游戏画面完全手绘而成，银河恶魔城风格的超大地图，快节奏富有挑战的动作风格，以每个人成长中都会遭遇的内心恐惧为故事驱动徐徐为您展开。<br>主人公约翰在一个奇异的梦幻王国中醒来，内心中隐隐觉得，这仿佛是他最不愿意看到的地方，但他将不得不鼓起勇气，去直面自己内心的恐惧，并一路深入，寻找出路…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/07ffa43f70c832012de5d1ac477b94a2.poster.avif?t=1770118001\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/07ffa43f70c832012de5d1ac477b94a2.webm?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/07ffa43f70c832012de5d1ac477b94a2.mp4?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/bf86ae1b866a817a2892aadc1654b1ae.avif?t=1770118001\" width=592 height=75 /></span><br><br>借用约翰在这个奇幻王国觉醒的洞察力和奇异天赋，开始这一次的奥德赛情感探索之旅，探索“想法”深处的世界。<br>注意：您个人性格和念头导致的选择将迫使你在光明与黑暗中开辟自己的个人道路，同时切记，真相往往和表面上看起来完全不同。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/a31ba93834721d9b6a7081b7aff8a4fe.poster.avif?t=1770118001\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/a31ba93834721d9b6a7081b7aff8a4fe.webm?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/a31ba93834721d9b6a7081b7aff8a4fe.mp4?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/9b287e40f36ecba2d5249daa38484cf9.avif?t=1770118001\" width=592 height=75 /></span><br><br>顶着新获得的奇怪脑袋和神来之笔，大开脑洞，头脑扫描，挥笔战斗。 <br>不走寻常路，去发现遍布这个奇异世界各地的众多支线任务，遭遇各类奇奇怪怪的人物，你将永远好奇人类的内心到底藏了多少“见不得人”的东西。<br>黑暗但却养眼的超现实画面和场景处处都充满了秘密，形形色色的NPC奇特的个性不时会带来“惊喜”，都在等待着你去揭开它们的神秘面纱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/29388261ff00aadfd09709013f19e618.poster.avif?t=1770118001\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/29388261ff00aadfd09709013f19e618.webm?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/29388261ff00aadfd09709013f19e618.mp4?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/df9aef72928626b63729846c29de2e56.avif?t=1770118001\" width=592 height=75 /></span><br><br>约翰独特的“视角”和分析能力能让你发现有关 NPC、奇特物体和环境元素的隐藏信息。《神来之笔》这一独特的玩法模拟再现了人类思想的独特之处。漫游在人迹罕至的地方，扫描你周围的世界，正如念头一动，谁知道呢…你将在各种不为人知角落，发现一些改变你观点的东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/5df328e5278dc6e1dbf5aae0255dc57a.poster.avif?t=1770118001\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/5df328e5278dc6e1dbf5aae0255dc57a.webm?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/5df328e5278dc6e1dbf5aae0255dc57a.mp4?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/739f0fa7112750fefa39824c33ddd0c8.avif?t=1770118001\" width=592 height=75 /></span><br><br>快节奏的操控挑战、紧张的氛围、充满想象力的表现力。<br>人类内心的各种不安和恐惧，将化身游戏内约翰的将遭遇的各种敌人和Boss，奇怪的念头、不幸的遭遇，都有可能成为你所面临的对手的外表甚至武器，这些都象征着人类心理的深不可测。<br>游戏中的有些战斗或者游戏挑战甚至会让你怀疑自己存在的现实感…<br>但请记住，只有你害怕，你才会恐惧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/d00dc5985017ff683910e67526852f23.poster.avif?t=1770118001\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/d00dc5985017ff683910e67526852f23.webm?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858810/extras/d00dc5985017ff683910e67526852f23.mp4?t=1770118001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>为什么说 “人生就像一支铅笔”</strong><br>铅笔削尖才能使用，人生磨砺才能成长。<br>铅笔 书写、绘画或涂鸦 ；内心 探索、调整或创造。<br>笔尖偶尔会断 人生间或失控<br>落笔有时会错 内心总有波折 <br>笔写下为记，人经历为忆。<br>祝所有不同的人生都找到自己的意义。",
